### External Extract Preview
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dynamic-views/external-extract/preview
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "dataSourceId": 1,
  "sql": "select 1 as id, 'demo' as name",
  "limit": 50
}

### Publish Physical View
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dynamic-views/orders_view/publish-physical
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-App-Id: {{appId}}

{
  "replaceIfExists": true,
  "physicalViewName": "vw_orders_view",
  "dataSourceId": 1,
  "comment": "P2 publish"
}

